This repository is source-available, not open source.

Valen Systems Inc. is making this code visible so trusted builders, prospective contributors, contractors, collaborators, and developers may inspect, run, study, and improve the Core interface under controlled terms.

This license exists to protect the Company’s strategic position while still creating a serious pathway for builders to help advance Core by Valen Systems.

Core is being built to give operators more capability, more control, and less dependence on incumbent dashboard-based software. The Company believes powerful software should become easier to use, not harder; more useful to ordinary operators, not more trapped behind vendors, dashboards, and technical gatekeeping.

That mission requires openness to builders, but it also requires discipline around ownership, commercialization, and distribution.

